        SELECT 1
        FROM [PLANILLA_REGISTRO_EMPRESA] AS [p]
        INNER JOIN [PLANILLA] AS [p0] ON [p].[ID_PLANILLA] = [p0].[ID]
        INNER JOIN [USUARIO] AS [u] ON [p0].[ID_USUARIO] = [u].[ID]
